&lt;p&gt;You’ll be doing more than just coding—you’ll collaborate closely with Product Designers, Analysts, and Engineering peers to create an engaging product experience that connects millions globally.&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;This role has &lt;strong&gt;high growth&lt;/strong&gt; opportunities, including expanding responsibility in leading engineering teams. Therefore, &lt;strong&gt;adaptability and eagerness to learn&lt;/strong&gt; are essential qualities we&#39;re after.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As well as being surrounded by other dedicated and talented software engineers and teams, we aim to provide an environment that promotes open discussion to solving &lt;strong&gt;complex problems&lt;/strong&gt;, and encourages engineers to &lt;strong&gt;learn new technologies and techniques&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pushpay’s environment allows for learning, making mistakes, contributing to the team and taking ownership.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we would like to see&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
