&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5+ years of software engineering experience, with proficiency in .NET/C#&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience in architecture, design, creation and delivery of solutions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
