&lt;p&gt;Drive the migration of legacy frontends into the &lt;strong&gt;modern React ecosystem&lt;/strong&gt;, improving maintainability, performance, and developer experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scaling Our Design System&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expand and evolve a &lt;strong&gt;shared component library and design system&lt;/strong&gt; used by multiple product teams across the organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Building a Unified Frontend Platform&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Help build a &lt;strong&gt;centralised frontend portal&lt;/strong&gt; from the ground up and establish integration patterns that allow domain teams to plug in seamlessly.&lt;/p&gt;
